===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|wepen|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|wepan|wēpan|to weep, complain, bewail, mourn over, deplore|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro}} {{recons|wōpijaną||to weep|lang=gem-pro}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro}} {{recons|wāb-||to call, cry, complain|lang=ine-pro}}. Cognate with {{etyl|sco|-}} {{term|wepe|lang=sco}}, {{term|weip||to weep|lang=sco}}, {{etyl|stq|-}} {{term|wapia||to cry, complain|lang=stq}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{term|æpa||to yell, shout|lang=is}}.

